            "1️⃣ You'd transfer the **C9** to your alternate account.\n\n"
            "2️⃣ Then, on your main account, you'd pick any blueprint that's also stored in **Pool 15** (i.e., **TANTTO .22 \"FISSION\"**) and perform the pull exploit.\n\n"
